Opinion Reward Converter Fast - Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy describes how Opinion Reward Converter Fast ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and protects user information. By using the Opinion Reward Converter Fast mobile application (the "App") and the services provided by the App (the "Services"), you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully to understand how we handle your information.

1. Information We Collect

1.1. User Account Details: To facilitate the conversion of Google Reward Money to real money and process payments, we collect and store certain user account details, including but not limited to Google account information, payment information, and transaction history.

1.2. User Information: We may collect information that you voluntarily provide, such as your name, email address, and other contact details, for communication and support purposes.

1.3. Device Information: We may automatically collect information about your device, including your device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers.

2. How We Use Your Information

2.1. Payment Processing: We use user account details to process payments for the conversion of Google Reward Money to real money.

2.2. Communication: We may use your contact information to communicate with you, respond to inquiries, and provide support.

2.3. Improvement of Services: We may use user information and device information to analyze usage patterns, enhance the functionality of the App, and improve our Services.

3. Data Security

3.1. We take reasonable measures to protect user information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

3.2. While we strive to protect user data, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information.

4. Third-Party Services

4.1. We may use third-party payment processors to facilitate payment transactions. These third-party processors have their own privacy policies, and we encourage users to review those policies before providing payment information.

5. Data Retention

5.1. We retain user account details and transaction history for as long as necessary to provide the Services and comply with legal obligations.

6. Sharing of Information

6.1. We do not sell or rent user information to third parties. However, we may share user information with trusted third parties to:

Facilitate payment processing.
Comply with legal obligations.
Protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property.
7. Changes to Privacy Policy

7.1. We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for legal reasons. We will notify users of any material changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy within the App.

8. Contact Information

8.1. If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at opinionrewardconvertor@gmail.com.

By using Opinion Reward Converter Fast, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to the collection, use, and sharing of your information as described herein. Your continued use of the App and Services constitutes your acceptance of this Privacy Policy and any future revisions.
